{
  "stem": "11671.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came across this word in my dictionary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I decided mental balance, that's the key to everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I'm going to remember my past, and make sure that it's not going to happen again, and try speaking about it, and teach the Holocaust lesson.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the same time, be happy and live every day to the fullest and just not to let that stop me from being happy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I found that just by going out to speaking to groups-- and I've spoken to schools and organizations and garden clubs and art, and B'nai B'rith, and Hadas.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You name it, all the organizations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was doing it in Chicago, and then when we lived in Florida, and also in Houston, and a little bit now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found that, that it's so important, that even if it's hard for me to do it, and it refreshes memories, and it brings back thoughts that I don't want to think about every day-- you cannot think about the Holocaust every day of your life.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you do, you do not exist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You destroy yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you have to just kind of put it aside and say, OK, now this happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to prevent it from happening, educate people, get them involved, stop the little things that-- the wrong thing that happens at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But don't live with it every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
